    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessimus nos domnus
                            <rs key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName key="#Marquis/duke" ref="#people/158">Gisolfus</persName> summus
                            <rs key="#Marquis/duke">dux</rs> gentis Langubardorum, <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/2002" key="#Intercessory">Scauniperge</persName>
                        gloriose dilecte coniuge nostre, tibi <persName ref="#people/3450"
                            key="#Abbots">Rimecausi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs> patri nostro de <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterio</rs><orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3413"
                            key="#Monasteries"> Sancti Stephani</orgName> qui fundatum est in
                            <placeName ref="#places/5009"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors #Slave"
                            >Strata</placeName>, <rs key="#Slave">pueros</rs> duos nomine <name
                            ref="Ursus">Urso</name> et <name ref="Ditentius">Ditentio</name> una cum
                        uxoribus, filios et filias suas,<rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Mention #Redistributive #Inflow #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                            > pro humicidium quem penetraverunt</rs>, solas eorum personas, et
                        fuerunt de <rs key="#Actio">actu</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Fiscal_property #Actio" ref="#places/260"
                            >Canusino</placeName> quam modo <persName key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus"
                            ref="#people/3498">Theutpald</persName>
                        <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">gastaldio</rs> nostro tenere videtur,
                        quatenus amodo et deinceps habeas et in tuo <rs key="#Servitium"
                            >servitium</rs> deteneat tam tu qui supra Rimecause et quicquid de eam
                        facere voluerit in tua sint in omnibus potestatem, et nullus ex nostris
                        gastaldiis aut actionariis nec quisquam homo contraque nostram potestas
                        quandoque ire presumat, sed nostram concessionem omni in tempore roborata
                        permaneat. Quod vero preceptum concessionis ex iussu et dictatum nominati
                        gloriosi domni nostri Gisolfi scripsi ego <persName key="#Notary"
                            ref="#people/3497">Iohanne</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, data iussione in hunc nostrum sacratissimum
                            <placeName ref="#places/110" key="#Cities">Beneventanum</placeName>
                        palatium mense martio, per indictionem quinta decimam. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
